Package heap

Class HFPage

java.lang.Object
diskmgr.Page
heap.HFPage
All Implemented Interfaces:
GlobalConst
Direct Known Subclasses:
BTSortedPage
public class HFPage
extends Page
implements GlobalConst
Class heap file page. The design assumes that records are kept compacted when deletions are performed.
